videos.headline: Newton toe taps for the Washington TD
videos.description: Washington's Jacob Eason finds Richard Newton who just keeps his feet in bounds for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Newton toe taps for the Washington TD) 2019/09/19

videos.headline: Eason zips pass to Fuller for the Huskies TD
videos.description: Washington's Jacob Eason throws a dart to WR Aaron Fuller for the 17-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Eason zips pass to Fuller for the Huskies TD) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: Washington gets long TD off fumble
videos.description: BYU quarterback Zach Wilson is sacked then fumbles, it is recovered by Washington's Brandon Wellington who goes 72 yards for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Washington gets long TD off fumble) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: Esukpa powers in for BYU TD
videos.description: Emmanuel Esukpa stays on top of the pile and falls into the end zone for the 1-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Esukpa powers in for BYU TD) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: BYU stuffs Washington's fake FG attempt
videos.description: Washington's holder Race Porter tries to run the fake but is stopped well short of the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU stuffs Washington's fake FG attempt) 2019/09/21

videos.headline: Washington's Fuller houses 89-yard punt return
videos.description: Washington's Aaron Fuller shows off the speed returning the punt 89 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Bushman hauls in BYU TD off the deflection
videos.description: Zach Wilson throws a dart, but it is almost intercepted and then caught by BYU's Matt Bushman.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bushman hauls in BYU TD off the deflection) 2019/09/21
